rows.label: tev002101_MSG0001
rows.name:
I don't get it. Nelson's team was full of talented
BLADEs, and they were even outfitted with a Skell![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0002
rows.name:
Make sure you're well-prepared before you go.
Your destination is in the eastern part of Primordia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0003
rows.name:
I think Lao's team is installing a data probe near the
land bridge that connects Primordia to Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0004
rows.name:
I know Lao's not the most pleasant guy to be around,
but he's a hell of a shot with a sniper rifle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0005
rows.name: You probably want to stop by and introduce yourself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0006
rows.name:
From the intel we've received, it sounds like the
Ganglion regiment over there is more like a battalion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0007
rows.name:
But I know you guys will figure out a way to get Irina's
team out of there. We're counting on you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0008
rows.name:
By the way, Lao's team, who we sent on ahead of you,
haven't been making their scheduled check-ins.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0009
rows.name:
When you join up with Lao, tell him I said to stop
blowing off his damn status reports already.
And also tell him that it's a damn order![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0019
rows.name:
Our mimeosomes have almost hit their limits.
If you can't get that data back from Lao,
it's see-ya-in-hell time for the whole human race.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0020
rows.name:
I need you to chase after Lao, give him what he's got
coming, and get that data back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0021
rows.name:
Cutting out the brain has taken a lot of the fight out of
the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0022
rows.name:
But there are still plenty of Ganglion loyalists out
there who are more desperate than ever.
Not to mention the freakin' swarms of indigens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0023
rows.name:
BLADE has a lot more work to do before we can
call this mission accomplished.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002101_MSG0024
rows.name:
If you want to start taking it a little easier, that's fine.
But don't you go telling yourself this is over.
Because it ain't. Not by a long shot.[ST:wait ]
